      "span_text": "Blood was drawn in 10-mL glass tubes containing glutathione and EGTA, and plasma catecholamines were measured by radioenzymatic technique according to Peuler and Johnson, 23 as reported previously.  24 All of the samples were analyzed by the same blinded technician.",
